<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Absent2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Absént,</orth> vb. refl. to keep far, to abstain: <cit><quote>that I should yet a. me from your bed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.2.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 125.</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>a. thee from felicity awhile,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 358</bibl></cit>.
